@endpoint POST /greengrass/groups
@desc Creates a group. You may provide the initial version of the group or use ''CreateGroupVersion'' at a later time. Tip: You can use the ''gg_group_setup'' package (https://github.com/awslabs/aws-greengrass-group-setup) as a library or command-line application to create and deploy Greengrass groups.
